    {
        "content": "<p>I believe if the diagram arises from a diagram of (small) sites, then the colimit looks something like small sheaves on a large site. Compare with Moerdijk's _Continuous fibrations and inverse limits of toposes_ <a href=\"http://www.numdam.org/item/CM_1986__58_1_45_0/\">http://www.numdam.org/item/CM_1986__58_1_45_0/</a></p>",
